title: General Census Stats by Census Tract for Salt Lake City, Utah, 2000
name: General Census Stats by Census Tract for Salt Lake City, Utah, 2000
description:
This datasets displays data from the US Census Bureau. The data in particular covers the Census Tracts of Salt Lake County in Utah for the 2000 US Census.

The data includes: Tract, total population 2000, Total Households 2000, Average Family Size 2000, Total Housing Units 2000, Median household income in 1999, Per capita income in 1999, Income in 1999 below poverty level, % of Population with Income in 1999 below poverty level, Income in 1999 at or above poverty level, % of population with Income in 1999 at or above poverty level
